snippet.title: Mindset - Official Trailer | Upload VR Showcase 2023
snippet.description:
Solve cube-shaped puzzles and uncover a cryptic story in VR puzzle game, Mindset. Watch the trailer to see some Mindset gameplay, a glimpse of the game's Challenge Mode, and more. Mindset is coming to Meta Quest 2 on June 29, 2023.

#SummerOfGaming #VR
